Package: PenalizedAD
Type: Package
Title: Penalized method for anomaly detection
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 22.12.2017
Author: AMVA4NewPhysics Authors
Maintainer: Grzegorz Kotkowski <grzegorzmichal.kotkowski@studenti.unipd.it>
Description: The package provides the implementation of the penalized approach for model-based clustering (MAES) and anomaly detection (PAD) introduced in the referenced document.
    It contains synthetic data examples used in simulations to test the algorithm.
License: GPL-3
References:  Working paper on a Statistical Learning method for Model-Independent searches for New Physics - AMVA4NewPhysics ITN
